headline: CDW to Announce Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2024 Results on February 5
summary: VERNON HILLS, Ill., January 22, 2025--CDW Corporation (Nasdaq: CDW), a leading multi-brand provider of information technology solutions to business, government, education and healthcare customers in the United States, the United Kingdom and Canada, today announced that it will host a webcast conference call to discuss its fourth quarter and full year 2024 results on Wednesday, February 5, 2025, at 7:30 a.m. CT/8:30 a.m. ET.
